  "publisher": "dc",
  "about": "Maxima is a character appearing in American comic books published by DC Comics. She is a morally ambiguous queen, alien conqueror from the planet Almerac. Known for her obsession with Superman, she views him as the only man worthy to be her mate and king. Despite her beginnings as a despot, she later reformed herself to become a superheroine who has also served as a member of the Justice League.",
